raw_text = "~ start
Naomi: Heyy Mabel, you got a sec? 😊
PlayerM: Always! What's up?
Naomi: Okay so I have something to tell you
Naomi: And I need you to hear me out before you freak out 😂
PlayerM: That's literally the scariest way to start a conversation Naomi 😰
Naomi: I know I know
Naomi: So you know how I do modeling work on the side right?
PlayerM: Yeah?
Naomi: Well I got booked for a shoot this Saturday
Naomi: A nude photoshoot 🤭
PlayerM: Oh wow okay 😳
Naomi: Well here's the thing
Naomi: It was supposed to be me and Caleb
Naomi: But Suzanna needed him for something urgent so he can't make it
PlayerM: Oh no 😕
PlayerM: So you need to find someone else?
PlayerM: Waaait, is that what my boyfriend volunteered for!?
Naomi: Yeah 🤣
PlayerM: ...
PlayerM: Naomi 🥺
PlayerM: NAOMI 😭
PlayerM: 😱😱😱
Naomi: SEE this is exactly why I said don't freak out 😂
PlayerM: How am I supposed to NOT freak out!?
PlayerM: My boyfriend is going to be NAKED
PlayerM: With YOU
Naomi: Girl breathe 😂
Naomi: I promise it's just professional work okay?
Naomi: It's for a softcore college magazine
PlayerM: NUDE! 😭
Naomi: Listen
Naomi: He won't be showing his face
Naomi: And I'll be directing the whole thing so nothing weird is gonna happen, pinky promise
Naomi: You trust me right? That's why I'm out here telling you lovely
PlayerM: Of course I trust you...
PlayerM: It's just
PlayerM: I don't know how to feel about it 🙈
Naomi: That's totally fair
Naomi: But think about it this way
Naomi: He didn't know what he was signing up for and I didn't want to feel like I tricked him into this
Naomi: That's why I'm telling you both within the same day
Naomi: I know he's respectful and I feel safe with him too!
PlayerM: Okay that's actually really sweet 🥺
Naomi: Right?
Naomi: And honestly he was worried about you and so I wanted to do the girl talk
Naomi: He definitely wouldn't do it if you weren't okay with it
PlayerM: I believe it 🥺🩷
Naomi: Mhm!
Naomi: So it's really up to you girl
PlayerM: Ughh
PlayerM: I mean...
PlayerM: Could I maybe do it?
Naomi: The shoot?
Naomi: Do you want to get in front of the camera naked? 😜
PlayerM: Nonono not naked
PlayerM: If you both feel comfortable with it then
PlayerM: I guess I can try to be okay with it? 😣
Naomi: That's my girl 🤗
Naomi: And hey
Naomi: Can I tell you a small secret?
Naomi: Something that I haven't even told my closest friends?
PlayerM: What 😳
Naomi: I was really afraid of losing your trust about this
Naomi: I lost my sister's trust because of a vile trick orchestrated by one of the sorority girls
Naomi: That's why I'm honest about everything now
PlayerM: What happened??
Naomi: I have a sister in the sorority and.. it's no use talking to her anymore
Naomi: I broke her heart and I haven't gotten over it until now
PlayerM: I'm sorry to hear that Naomi 🥺
PlayerM: If it makes you feel better, I think of you as a big sis 😊
Naomi: Awwh, I think of you as my little sis too
Naomi: I'd seriously squeeze you all tight right now
PlayerM: No way, your boobs are bigger than mine ☺️
Naomi: Haha shush, I saw a little of you and I was impressed 😍
PlayerM: Stop omg 🙈
PlayerM: Is Caleb okay with you doing stuff like that?
Naomi: Caleb has zero issues with it!
Naomi: He actually said your boyfriend seems like a stand-up guy
PlayerM: Caleb is so sweet 😭
Naomi: He really is
PlayerM: I guess me and babe could learn a bit from you two ☺️
Naomi: Awwh you're such a darling
Naomi: So we're good? 😊
PlayerM: Yeah, of course. Thanks for explaining it to me 😊
PlayerM: But uhm..
PlayerM: I want to see the photos before, is that okay?
Naomi: Deal! 😘
Naomi: You might actually like them hehe
PlayerM: NAOMI 🙈
PlayerM: I'm not a perv... I don't think..
Naomi: What! I'm just saying 😇
Naomi: Alright I gotta go prep some stuff
Naomi: Love you girl ❤️
PlayerM: Love you too 🩷
PlayerM: Even though you're trying to give me a heart attack 🫠
Naomi: That's what big sisters are for 😘
Naomi: Full of surprises!
=> END"
